preference.name: TraceReport_Filter_Available_Object_Types
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of available object types under the Available Object Types heading that you can select for filtering when setting object type filters. You set object type filters by clicking the Object Type Filters tab in the Trace Links view or Traceview Settings dialog box. From this list, you select the object types that you want to display in the in the Trace Links view. Valid Values: String values.
